{"pageProps":{"id":["lang/go/basic/ptr.adoc"],"postInfo":{"type":"adoc","doc":{"title":"Go: 指针","author":"weily","tags":[],"version":"1.0","date":1590422400000,"content":"<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>Go 语言有指针类型，没想到吧。指针的值是一个内存地址。类型 <code>*T</code> 是一个指向 <code>T</code> 值的指针。指针的零值是 <code>nil</code>。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>可以像下面这这样声明一个指针：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">var</span> p *<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// p 是指向 int 值的指针</span></code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>使用操作符 <code>&amp;</code>（取地址操作符）来获取一个值的地址。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\">i := <span class=\"hljs-number\">42</span>\np = &amp;i</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>使用操作符 <code>*</code>（解引用操作符）表示指针所指向的值。比如：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-go\" data-lang=\"go\">fmt.Println(*p) <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 通过指针 p 读取 i 的值</span>\n*p = <span class=\"hljs-number\">21</span>         <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 通过指针 p 设置 i 的值</span></code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>"},"toc":{"type":"simple","title":"Go 语言基础","description":"这里是 Go 语言 XXXXXX","toc":[{"title":"基础","path":"basic.adoc"},{"title":"函数","path":"func.adoc"},{"title":"变量","path":"var.adoc"},{"title":"基本类型","path":"basic-types.adoc"},{"title":"字符串","path":"string.adoc"},{"title":"指针","path":"ptr.adoc"},{"title":"数组和切片","path":"array-slice.adoc"},{"title":"映射","path":"map.adoc"},{"title":"结构：struct","path":"struct.adoc"},{"title":"接口：interface","path":"itf.adoc"},{"title":"type 关键字","path":"type.adoc"},{"title":"for 语句","path":"for.adoc"},{"title":"if 语句","path":"if.adoc"},{"title":"switch 语句","path":"switch.adoc"},{"title":"defer 语句","path":"defer.adoc"},{"title":"并发","path":"concurrency.adoc"},{"title":"包和导入","path":"pkg-import.adoc"}]}}},"__N_SSG":true}